<div class='media__message'>
<h4 class='h12 talk-link__speaker'>앤더스 프젤버그</h4>
<h4 class='h9 m5'>
<a class='' href='http://www.ted.com/talks/anders_fjellberg_two_nameless_bodies_washed_up_on_the_beach_here_are_their_stories?language=ko' lang='ko'>
해변에 쓸려온 이름 모르는 두 시신. 그 사연을 들려드립니다
</a>
</h4>
<div class='meta'>
<span class='meta__item'>
Posted
<span class='meta__val'>
Oct 2015
</span>
</span>
<span class='meta__row'>
Rated
<span class='meta__val'>
Informative, Courageous
</span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
